John D. NAGLE, as Commissioner of Immigration for the Port of San Francisco, Appellant, v. HOM BING WAH and Hom War Fung, Appellees. No. 5988. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 25, 1930.

Before RUDKIN, DIETRICH, and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Motion of appellant granted, and appeal dismissed.
